Since you listen to show suggestions, I was wondering if you could check out Reign sometime? It’s a historical drama based around the life of Mary Queen of Scots. It was my introduction to historical dramas, and I still love it to death. Something that’s especially fun for me is seeing how much Mary changed since the pilot episode. By the end of season 4, she’s a completely different person.

It doessss have disturbing (and potentially traumatizing) events, so beware of that.
